[+] Run directly
-------------------------------

  felcon can be executed directly (unpack tarball, enter felcon directory).

  # sh felcon
  or
  # ./felcon

  Root privileges are preferred for full audits.



[+] Installation
-------------------------------

  If you want to install felcon, see the README file (section: Installation) for
  more tips about how to install or create a custom package.

  Packages are available via https://packages.cisofy.com



[+] Documentation
-------------------------------

  Documentation about felcon can be found in the man page (man felcon, or
  felcon --man-page), README file and website. Also the FAQ file covers some
  often asked questions.


